{"tid":1004183,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［伸手黨］有無人可以深入淺出咁講下咩係牛熊同點買？","createTime":"2019-02-01T08:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T12:07:25.000Z","uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"15f737edba5972f7e24bb48101fed2ea7bb48fbe","tid":1004183,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ada56d82f1d8dc6e9af4e4c726ecb36d917ed9","tid":1004183,"uid":2267,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jLpVvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jLpVvR.png&h=f2f4ab23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛，喺地球上，屬於草食性動物，一般都唔會主動攻擊人類，性格比較溫順。<br />\n如要買牛嘅肉，可到各大超市或各區街市有售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEyGdiv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEyGdiv.png&h=8263ee89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熊，喺地球上，有分具攻擊性同無攻擊性。先唔講攻擊性嘅熊，就講圖中來自日本熊本縣嘅吉祥物。日語名稱為「くまモン」，英文名稱是Kumamon，官方中文名其實是「酷MA萌」。<br />\n「酷MA萌」，深受老少咸宜喜愛，如要購買，可到日本熊本縣精品店或本港精品店內有售。"},{"pid":"23584fa5fd5ee6a8e85ac7952d511ac48007c969","tid":1004183,"uid":68867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"識 牛牛吽 同 熊熊哈 就ok了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e0193684baf86a03c060ae0d131df00036f50a","tid":1004183,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:50:34.000Z","msg":"So9sad. <br />\n做伸手黨失敗。<br />\n有無邊位ching 平時喂開人食野既教路下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d9183bb42314a901b0cad052a688f211791233","tid":1004183,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"禮拜一all in熊過年 新年返黎睇樓"},{"pid":"8ee18